events.name: Penn State Nittany Lions at Ohio State Buckeyes

video.headline: Ohio State looks like No. 1 team in win over Penn State

headlines.shortLinkText: Barrett plays finisher as No. 1 Ohio St beats Penn St 38-10

events.name: West Virginia Mountaineers at Baylor Bears

headlines.description: Corey Coleman caught three more touchdowns and second-ranked Baylor won its FBS-best 19th consecutive home game, getting some measure of revenge with a 62-38 victory over West Virginia.
headlines.shortLinkText: Coleman 3 TD catches for No. 2 Baylor in 62-38 win over WVU

events.name: TCU Horned Frogs at Iowa State Cyclones

headlines.description: Trevone Boykin threw for 436 yards and four touchdowns and third-ranked TCU rolled past Iowa State 45-21 Saturday for its third road win in four weeks.

video.headline: Boykin fuels TCU past Iowa State

headlines.shortLinkText: Boykin throws for 4 TDs, No. 3 TCU rolls past Iowa St 45-21

events.name: Arizona State Sun Devils at Utah Utes

headlines.description: Travis Wilson threw for 297 yards and two touchdown and No. 4 Utah held off Arizona State 34-18 on Saturday night to remain the lone undefeated team in the Pac-12.

video.headline: Utah rallies past Arizona State, stays unbeaten

headlines.shortLinkText: No. 4 Utah beats Arizona State 34-18 to remain undefeated

events.name: Boston College Eagles at Clemson Tigers

events.name: Florida Gators at LSU Tigers

headlines.shortLinkText: Fake FG keys No. 6 LSU's win over No. 8 Florida

events.name: Michigan State Spartans at Michigan Wolverines

events.name: Alabama Crimson Tide at Texas A&M Aggies

headlines.description: Derrick Henry ran for a career-high 236 yards and two scores and No. 10 Alabama added a school-record three touchdowns on interception returns to get a 41-23 win over No. 9 Texas A&M on Saturday.

events.name: Louisville Cardinals at Florida State Seminoles

events.name: USC Trojans at Notre Dame Fighting Irish

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Helton after USC-Notre Dame) 2015/10/17 SC

events.name: Iowa Hawkeyes at Northwestern Wildcats

headlines.shortLinkText: No. 19 Oklahoma shuts out Kansas State 55-0

events.name: Eastern Michigan Eagles at Toledo Rockets

events.name: Louisiana Tech Bulldogs at Mississippi State Bulldogs

headlines.shortLinkText: Offensive quartet leads Southern Miss over UTSA 32-10
